Matrix
Graph adjacency matrix
DP
Use ARRAYLIST when:

✅ Dynamic size
✅ Frequent reads/access
✅ General-purpose list

Examples:

Most enterprise apps
APIs
LeetCode
Use LINKEDLIST when:

✅ Frequent head/tail operations
✅ Queue/deque implementations
